                  <li>
                    <p>
                      If <m>P</m> and <m>Q</m> are the same point, then <m>d(P,Q) = 0</m>.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <p>
                      If <m>d(P,Q) = 0</m>, then <m>P</m> and <m>Q</m> are the same point.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
