          and a taxi is hailed at point <m>P</m> to travel to point <m>Q</m>.
          In this situation, diagonal movement is impossible,<fn>
          Maybe <sq>discouraged</sq> or <sq>difficult</sq> would be better word choices.
          </fn> so the taxi is limited to traveling horizontally and vertically.
